          "content": "# Campaigns Above 30% ACOS and Optimization Priorities\n\nQuestion: Show me campaigns with ACOS above 30% and analyze from which dimensions they should be optimized.\n\nBusiness data used: campaign-level advertising performance, campaign configuration, budget, and status snapshots. Time basis: 2025-04-01/2025-04-30; 2025-04-01/2025-04-29; 2025-04-01/2025-04-27. Monetary values follow the numeric currency basis present in the business data; no additional FX conversion was applied.\n\n## Campaigns above 30% ACOS\n\n| campaign | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| BU4A-小熊【床单组-竹纤维-素色-QU-鲍鱼壳灰】SP精准-bamboo sheets | $27,027.43 | $81,064.45 | 1,539 | 9,092 | 33.3% | 16.9% |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-荣芳【枕套组-全涤-素色-色丁-QU-白色】SP精准-satin pillo… | $15,115.66 | $43,332.55 | 4,330 | 12,936 | 34.9% | 33.5% |\n| BU3A-CJW【床单-竹纤维-素色-QU-灰】SP精准-cooling词根-已加购潜在人群-AMC受众B… | $14,996.06 | $47,773.95 | 939 | 5,489 | 31.4% | 17.1% |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-荣芳【枕套组-全涤-素色-色丁-QU-鹿皮米】SP精准-silk pillo… | $9,622.88 | $26,085.76 | 2,587 | 7,075 | 36.9% | 36.6% |\n| BU3A-荣芳【枕套组-全涤-素色-色丁-KI-灰色】SP精准-纯尺码词down only | $8,370.91 | $23,721.52 | 2,027 | 5,698 | 35.3% | 35.6% |\n| BU3A-荣芳【枕套组】SB精准-核心词(satin)-商品集-旗舰店@@SB-US000561GQU | $8,238.62 | $24,012.89 | 2,227 | 5,248 | 34.3% | 42.4% |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-CHY【床单-压花/深笠高/仿水洗棉】SB广泛-sheet+KI-商品集-旗… | $7,596.46 | $18,067.88 | 507 | 2,932 | 42.0% | 17.3% |\n| Xnurta AI BU3A-CHY【床单-压花/竹纤维/深笠高】SB精准-sheets+QU词根-商品集… | $7,390.75 | $17,373.81 | 613 | 3,141 | 42.5% | 19.5% |\n| BU3A-GH【被子-锦氨-双面凉感-QU-港湾灰】SP精准-Cooling Blanket词根-Top位 | $7,062.93 | $16,234.35 | 212 | 2,356 | 43.5% | 9.0% |\n| BU3A-荣芳【枕套组-全涤-素色-色丁拉链款-ST-鹿皮米】SP精准-satin+词根-企业购boost | $6,827.59 | $13,563.36 | 1,446 | 4,694 | 50.3% | 30.8% |\n\nThere are 309 campaigns with ACOS above 30% and non-zero sales in the full-period business metrics. The highest-priority fixes are the campaigns with both high spend and weak conversion economics, because they can move account ACOS fastest.\n\n## Optimization dimensions\n\n1. Keyword/search-term quality: pull search terms for these campaigns and separate converting terms from high-spend/no-order terms.\n2. Bid level: reduce bids 15-30% where ACOS is high but orders still exist; pause only after confirming the term is not strategically defensive.\n3. Match type: move profitable broad/phrase queries into exact match and cap the exploratory budget.\n4. Product/ASIN fit: check whether the advertised ASIN is relevant to the winning query; poor query-ASIN fit is a common cause of high clicks and weak sales.\n5. Placement: add placement reporting before changing top-of-search multipliers; this business data does not contain placement-level sales/ACOS.\n6. Budget allocation: shift budget away from high-spend/high-ACOS campaigns into campaigns below target ACOS or with higher CVR.\n\n## Extra 业务数据 needed\n\nFor precise bid recommendations, I still need current keyword bids, search-term-level performance for these same campaigns, and placement-level sales/ACOS.\n"
