          "label": "C",
          "content": "# The 10 Keywords Most in Need of Optimization\n\nQuestion: Analyze the 10 keywords that most need to be optimized.\n\nBusiness data used: campaign-level advertising performance, keyword, search-term, and targeting performance, campaign configuration, budget, and status snapshots. Time basis: 2026-04-08 to 2026-05-07. Monetary values follow the numeric currency basis present in the business data; no additional FX conversion was applied.\n\n## Executive read\n\nFrom the available business data, measurable totals are spend $54,508.56, sales $280,859.28, orders 5,829, clicks 40,466, and aggregate ACOS 19.4%. The answer below uses the most relevant dimensions present in the business data; missing fields are called out explicitly.\n\n## Key keyword/search term view\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| cooling mats for dogs | $2,611.15 | $10,110.90 | 185 | 1,520 | 25.8% | 12.2% |\n| dog cooling mat | $2,235.68 | $14,958.59 | 251 | 1,668 | 14.9% | 15.0% |\n| green pet | $2,207.00 | $31,125.38 | 531 | 1,854 | 7.1% | 28.6% |\n| cooling mat for dogs | $1,991.10 | $7,997.98 | 147 | 1,138 | 24.9% | 12.9% |\n| cooling mat dogs | $1,897.41 | $6,296.70 | 117 | 1,012 | 30.1% | 11.6% |\n| cooling mat for dog | $1,626.04 | $6,493.00 | 122 | 960 | 25.0% | 12.7% |\n| loose-match | $1,605.92 | $5,630.19 | 45 | 1,910 | 28.5% | 2.4% |\n| gun safe | $1,265.84 | $897.34 | 7 | 328 | 141.1% | 2.1% |\n\n## Scale candidates\n\nThese have orders and controlled ACOS, so they are the safer places to add incremental traffic:\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| green pet | $2,207.00 | $31,125.38 | 531 | 1,854 | 7.1% | 28.6% |\n| dog cooling mat | $2,235.68 | $14,958.59 | 251 | 1,668 | 14.9% | 15.0% |\n| cooling mats for dogs | $2,611.15 | $10,110.90 | 185 | 1,520 | 25.8% | 12.2% |\n| cooling mat for dogs | $1,991.10 | $7,997.98 | 147 | 1,138 | 24.9% | 12.9% |\n| hornady | $857.26 | $7,367.25 | 76 | 935 | 11.6% | 8.1% |\n| close-match | $1,245.66 | $7,220.43 | 73 | 1,290 | 17.3% | 5.7% |\n\n## Optimization / reduction candidates\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | recommended action |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| gun safe | $1,265.84 | $897.34 | 7 | 328 | 141.1% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| dog tooth wipes | $484.31 | $729.96 | 50 | 144 | 66.3% | monitor and test in a separate tier |\n| dog dental wipes | $366.59 | $318.28 | 25 | 124 | 115.2% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| paw wipes | $366.10 | $432.87 | 22 | 119 | 84.6% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| paw wipes for dogs | $349.51 | $384.12 | 23 | 138 | 91.0% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| gun safe for handgun | $312.18 | $415.90 | 2 | 133 | 75.1% | monitor and test in a separate tier |\n| guns safe | $212.67 | $242.98 | 2 | 115 | 87.5% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| wipes for dogs | $190.48 | $148.75 | 9 | 57 | 128.1% | lower bid and check relevance |\n\n## Recommendations\n\n1. Move low-ACOS, order-producing terms into exact match with controlled budgets.\n2. Negate or pause high-spend zero-order terms first.\n3. Cut bids 15-30% for terms with orders but materially high ACOS.\n4. Keep broad/phrase discovery capped, then migrate winners into exact.\n"
