      "question_zh": "请针对The Green Pet Shop创建一份报告，分析这个品线中，哪些关键词应该被添加为否定关键词，并帮助我建立一个否定关键词库。",
      "question_en": "Create a report for The Green Pet Shop analyzing which keywords in this product line should be added as negative keywords, and help me build a negative-keyword library.",
