          "label": "B",
          "content": "# Negative Keyword Library for The Green Pet Shop\n\nQuestion: Create a report for The Green Pet Shop analyzing which keywords in this product line should be added as negative keywords, and help me build a negative-keyword library.\n\nBusiness data used: campaign-level advertising performance, keyword, search-term, and targeting performance, campaign configuration, budget, and status snapshots. Time basis: 2025-01-01/2025-03-31; 2025-01-03/2025-03-31; 2025-01-03/2025-03-24. Monetary values follow the numeric currency basis present in the business data; no additional FX conversion was applied.\n\n## Executive read\n\nFrom the available business data, measurable totals are spend $343,008.48, sales $2,097,368.36, orders 54,498, clicks 467,196, and aggregate ACOS 16.4%. The answer below uses the most relevant dimensions present in the business data; missing fields are called out explicitly.\n\n## Period comparison\n\n| business view / period | rows | spend | sales | orders | ACOS | ROAS |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Business slice 1 | 843 | $171,504.24 | $1,048,684.18 | 27,249 | 16.4% | 6.11 |\n| Business slice 2 | 71,294 | $171,504.24 | $1,048,684.18 | 27,249 | 16.4% | 6.11 |\n\n## Key keyword/search term view\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| B08HVXKRTD | $1,347.01 | $7,296.00 | 346 | 1,287 | 18.5% | 26.9% |\n| dog wipes | $1,132.17 | $7,369.95 | 233 | 832 | 15.4% | 28.0% |\n| reduce kids tumbler | $1,026.02 | $5,693.53 | 289 | 2,281 | 18.0% | 12.7% |\n| hornady gun safe | $1,004.59 | $10,506.74 | 75 | 895 | 9.6% | 8.4% |\n| reduce tumbler | $838.40 | $1,943.64 | 104 | 1,344 | 43.1% | 7.7% |\n| wall safe | $580.20 | $3,054.04 | 12 | 438 | 19.0% | 2.7% |\n| snow broom for car | $468.23 | $4,634.73 | 117 | 620 | 10.1% | 18.9% |\n| hornady rapid safe | $466.28 | $9,280.35 | 56 | 725 | 5.0% | 7.7% |\n\n## Scale candidates\n\nThese have orders and controlled ACOS, so they are the safer places to add incremental traffic:\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| hornady gun safe | $1,004.59 | $10,506.74 | 75 | 895 | 9.6% | 8.4% |\n| hornady rapid safe | $466.28 | $9,280.35 | 56 | 725 | 5.0% | 7.7% |\n| dog wipes | $1,132.17 | $7,369.95 | 233 | 832 | 15.4% | 28.0% |\n| B08HVXKRTD | $1,347.01 | $7,296.00 | 346 | 1,287 | 18.5% | 26.9% |\n| hornady rapid safe night guard | $183.50 | $6,543.04 | 33 | 355 | 2.8% | 9.3% |\n| reduce kids tumbler | $1,026.02 | $5,693.53 | 289 | 2,281 | 18.0% | 12.7% |\n\n## Optimization / reduction candidates\n\n| keyword/search term | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | recommended action |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| eva-dry gun safe dehumidifier | $93.92 | $149.78 | 6 | 199 | 62.7% | monitor and test in a separate tier |\n| lego pixel art | $34.76 | $0.00 | 0 | 39 | n/a | negate/pause or cut bid sharply |\n| pix brix wild kratts toy | $30.77 | $35.98 | 2 | 58 | 85.5% | lower bid and check relevance |\n| cat cooling mat | $30.57 | $49.99 | 1 | 46 | 61.2% | monitor and test in a separate tier |\n| billconch biometric gun safe | $23.39 | $0.00 | 0 | 8 | n/a | negate/pause or cut bid sharply |\n| gun safe for handgun quick-access handgun safes | $21.97 | $0.00 | 0 | 9 | n/a | negate/pause or cut bid sharply |\n| biometric gun safe for car | $21.93 | $0.00 | 0 | 5 | n/a | negate/pause or cut bid sharply |\n| vehicle gun safe | $20.87 | $0.00 | 0 | 27 | n/a | negate/pause or cut bid sharply |\n\n## Recommendations\n\n1. Move low-ACOS, order-producing terms into exact match with controlled budgets.\n2. Negate or pause high-spend zero-order terms first.\n3. Cut bids 15-30% for terms with orders but materially high ACOS.\n4. Keep broad/phrase discovery capped, then migrate winners into exact.\n"
