          "content": "# Keyword Winners and Negatives by Ad Type\n\nQuestion: Analyze which keywords perform well — including CTR, CVR, ACOS, orders — and which ad type they perform best in. Identify which keywords are worth continuing to invest in, and which keywords with low conversion and high ACOS should be negated.\n\nBusiness data used: 30-day keyword advertising performance with target keyword, match type, campaign name/ad type, impressions, clicks, spend, sales, and orders. Time basis: 2026-04-08 to 2026-05-07. Currency is USD as reported.\n\n## Executive read\n\nThis answer corrects the earlier parsing issue: spend is present in the keyword performance data. Totals are spend $52,591.06, sales $278,066.78, orders 5,846, and clicks 39,469.\n\n## Keywords to keep investing in\n\n| keyword | best ad type | match types | clicks | orders | CTR | CVR | ACOS | action |\n| --- | --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- |\n| green pet | SB | PHRASE | 1,859 | 534 | 1.93% | 28.7% | 7.1% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| dog cooling mat | SB | EXACT, PHRASE | 1,675 | 252 | 0.72% | 15.0% | 15.0% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| drop it wine drops | SB | EXACT, PHRASE | 354 | 178 | 3.82% | 50.3% | 7.9% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| cooling mat for dogs | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 1,141 | 148 | 0.86% | 13.0% | 24.7% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| cooling mat for dog | SP | EXACT | 961 | 124 | 0.72% | 12.9% | 24.6% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| drop it | SB | EXACT, PHRASE | 413 | 112 | 1.08% | 27.1% | 24.3% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| belly bone | SP | EXACT | 205 | 103 | 1.17% | 50.2% | 10.0% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n| arrow | SP | PHRASE | 278 | 97 | 1.06% | 34.9% | 11.2% | keep; move budget to exact/phrase and raise bids only if margin allows |\n\n## Keywords to reduce or negate\n\n| keyword | ad type | match types | clicks | orders | CTR | CVR | ACOS | action |\n| --- | --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- |\n| gun safe | SP | PHRASE | 331 | 7 | 0.30% | 2.1% | 141.7% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| dog dental wipes | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 124 | 26 | 0.49% | 21.0% | 111.0% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| paw wipes | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 119 | 22 | 0.40% | 18.5% | 84.6% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| paw wipes for dogs | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 141 | 23 | 0.36% | 16.3% | 92.2% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| guns safe | SP | PHRASE | 115 | 2 | 0.30% | 1.7% | 87.5% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| wipes for dogs | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 57 | 9 | 0.58% | 15.8% | 128.1% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| tooth wipes for dogs | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 51 | 8 | 0.65% | 15.7% | 148.7% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n| pet wipe | SP | EXACT, PHRASE | 46 | 9 | 0.75% | 19.6% | 114.1% | reduce bid or add negative at search-term level |\n"
