          "label": "B",
          "content": "# Keywords Where CPC Exceeds Bid\n\nQuestion: Keywords where the trailing-7-day CPC exceeds the keyword-level bid. (This should not normally happen — flag it and explain.)\n\nBusiness data used: trailing-7-day keyword CPC calculations joined to current keyword-level bid settings, including campaign, keyword, match type, clicks, total cost, average CPC, bid, CPC-to-bid ratio, and excess spend. Time basis follows the business data: 2026-05-01 to 2026-05-07 / 2026-05-02 to 2026-05-07 depending on row coverage. Currency is USD as reported.\n\n## Executive read\n\nThis answer removes the earlier parsing noise: sales/orders are not needed for this CPC-vs-bid check and are not shown as zero. I found 654 keyword rows where observed CPC exceeded the current keyword bid, with 5,598 clicks, $8,385.27 total cost, and $2,206.09 estimated spend above the bid ceiling. The highest-priority fixes are rows with both material excess dollars and meaningful clicks.\n\n| keyword | match | campaign | clicks | CPC | bid | CPC / bid | excess spend | explanation |\n| --- | --- | --- | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | ---: | --- |\n| cooling pad for dog | EXACT | GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 111 | $1.90 | $0.40 | 4.74x | $166.07 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| cooling mat dogs | EXACT | GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 505 | $1.94 | $1.77 | 1.09x | $83.36 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| cooling mat dogs | EXACT | GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 75 | $2.01 | $1.16 | 1.74x | $64.08 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| cooling mat for dogs | PHRASE | GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | 137 | $1.81 | $1.37 | 1.32x | $60.77 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| dog tooth wipes | EXACT | Petkin-Pet_Dental_Wipes-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 41 | $2.71 | $1.55 | 1.75x | $47.45 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| drop it | PHRASE | WineRX-Drop_It_Drops-MULTI-BRANDED-SP-PHRASE | 55 | $1.65 | $0.84 | 1.96x | $44.44 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| cooling mat for dogs | EXACT | GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 127 | $1.91 | $1.59 | 1.20x | $41.04 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| mat for dog | PHRASE | GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | 83 | $1.41 | $0.94 | 1.50x | $39.13 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| dog cool mat | PHRASE | GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | 67 | $1.51 | $0.96 | 1.58x | $36.99 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| case trimmer | PHRASE | Hornady-Reloading_Case_Trimmer-B000PD6QJ6-NB-SP-PHRASE | 88 | $1.82 | $1.43 | 1.27x | $34.26 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| cooling mat for dog | EXACT | GPS-GPetShop_Pet_Pad_Cover-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 86 | $1.13 | $0.77 | 1.47x | $31.28 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n| paw wipes for dogs | EXACT | Petkin-Paw_Wipes_Orange-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | 44 | $2.05 | $1.36 | 1.51x | $30.56 | likely bid changed after clicks, placement multiplier, dynamic bidding, or reporting/bid timing mismatch |\n\n## Actions\n\n1. Audit bid history and placement modifiers for the top excess-dollar rows first.\n2. If the current bid is intentional, cap the placement modifier or dynamic bidding rule so realized CPC cannot keep clearing above bid.\n3. If the bid was recently reduced, wait one reporting cycle before treating small-click rows as defects; prioritize high-click rows such as cooling mat dogs, cooling mat for dogs, and cooling pad for dog.\n4. For exact-match rows with high excess dollars, lower bid another 10%-20% or isolate into a controlled campaign until CPC normalizes.\n"
