          "content": "# Analysis of Weekly Spend by Ad Type (Last 8 Weeks)\n\n## Data Overview\n- **Period**: March 13, 2026, to May 8, 2026 (8 weeks)\n- **Account**: Firefly Buys\n- **Ad Types**: Sponsored Products (SP) and Sponsored Brands (SB) only. No spend recorded for Sponsored Display (SD).\n- **Status**: The account shows a significant decline in spend starting mid-April, with zero spend recorded in the final two weeks (W7 and W8).\n\n---\n\n## Weekly Spend Breakdown (USD)\n\n| Week | Date Range | SP Spend | SB Spend | SD Spend | Total Spend | SP % | SB % |\n|------|------------|---------:|---------:|---------:|------------:|-----:|-----:|\n| W1 | 03/13–03/19 | $64,627.03 | $3,401.70 | $0.00 | $68,028.73 | 95.0% | 5.0% |\n| W2 | 03/20–03/26 | $4,467.12 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $4,467.12 | 100.0% | 0.0% |\n| W3 | 03/27–04/02 | $17.03 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $17.03 | 100.0% | 0.0% |\n| W4 | 04/03–04/09 | $6,858.30 | $21.06 | $0.00 | $6,879.36 | 99.7% | 0.3% |\n| W5 | 04/10–04/16 | $1,190.34 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $1,190.34 | 100.0% | 0.0% |\n| W6 | 04/17–04/23 | $1,096.03 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $1,096.03 | 100.0% | 0.0% |\n| W7 | 04/24–04/30 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $0.00 | — | — |\n| W8 | 05/01–05/08 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $0.00 | $0.00 | — | — |\n| **Total** | | **$78,255.85** | **$3,422.76** | **$0.00** | **$81,678.61** | **95.8%** | **4.2%** |\n\n---\n\n## Structural Change Analysis\n\n### 1. Overall Trend\nThere is a **drastic contraction** in total spend. After a peak in Week 1 ($68k), spend dropped sharply and fluctuated at much lower levels before ceasing entirely in Weeks 7 and 8. This suggests either a major budget cut, campaign pauses, or an account-level suspension.\n\n### 2. Shift in Ad Type Mix\n- **SP Dominance**: Sponsored Products remain the primary ad type, accounting for 95–100% of the weekly mix.\n- **SB Phase-out**: Sponsored Brands spend was significant only in Week 1. It dropped to near zero by Week 4 and disappeared thereafter.\n- **SD Absence**: Sponsored Display was not utilized during this 8-week window.\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion and Direction\nThe advertising structure is **shifting toward total consolidation in SP before going dormant**.\n1. **Spend Direction**: Downward trend to zero.\n2. **Structural Direction**: Diversification is decreasing. The account is losing its SB presence and has no SD activity. \n3. **Recommendation**: If this dormancy is unintentional, investigate campaign statuses and payment methods immediately. If intentional, note that the current structure relies exclusively on SP, which may limit the ability to capture top-of-funnel or remarketing demand.\n"
