          "label": "C",
          "content": "# Account ACOS Change Decomposition\n\nQuestion: Account-level ACOS in the last 30 days vs. the prior 30. Decompose into changes in spend, sales, and compositional shifts. Identify the single biggest contributor.\n\nBusiness data used: campaign-level advertising performance, ad-product/ad-type performance across SP/SB/SD, campaign configuration, budget, and status snapshots。 Time basis: 2026-03-09/2026-04-07; 2026-04-08/2026-05-07; 2026-03-25/2026-04-07。 Notes: Includes current-period and comparison-period metrics。 Monetary values follow the numeric currency basis present in the business data; no additional FX conversion was applied.\n\nNote: This answer was regenerated using the richer ZH business data for the same question while keeping the output in English.\n\n## Executive Read\n\nUsing the richer business data for this question, measurable totals are spend $84,427.03, sales $467,725.64, orders 10,927, clicks 65,888, and aggregate ACOS 18.1%. The analysis below focuses on the most relevant campaign dimension for the question.\n\n## Period / Business View Comparison\n\n| business view / period | rows | spend | sales | orders | ACOS | ROAS |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Business slice 1 | 150 | $30,072.70 | $192,488.74 | 5,199 | 15.6% | 6.40 |\n| Business slice 2 | 148 | $54,354.33 | $275,236.90 | 5,728 | 19.7% | 5.06 |\n\n## Key campaign View\n\n| campaign | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | CVR |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $8,814.48 | $42,861.34 | 761 | 5,200 | 20.6% | 14.6% |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-Branded-SP-Phrase | $2,922.55 | $42,636.12 | 727 | 2,527 | 6.9% | 28.8% |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | $4,894.25 | $24,804.21 | 443 | 3,552 | 19.7% | 12.5% |\n| Petkin-BigNThick_Pet_Wipes_Large-MULTI-Branded-SP… | $2,530.85 | $15,278.01 | 701 | 1,728 | 16.6% | 40.6% |\n| GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $3,157.08 | $13,424.75 | 296 | 1,980 | 23.5% | 14.9% |\n| Arrow-CatchAll-MULTI-Branded-SP-Phrase | $1,140.61 | $13,246.08 | 585 | 1,376 | 8.6% | 42.5% |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Pet_Pads-MULTI-NB-SB-Exact | $1,359.96 | $11,212.19 | 173 | 787 | 12.1% | 22.0% |\n| WineRX-Drop_It_Drops-MULTI-BRANDED-SP-PHRASE | $1,618.31 | $9,343.68 | 439 | 1,385 | 17.3% | 31.7% |\n\n## Scale Candidates\n\n| campaign | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | recommendation |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $8,814.48 | $42,861.34 | 761 | 5,200 | 20.6% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-Branded-SP-Phrase | $2,922.55 | $42,636.12 | 727 | 2,527 | 6.9% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n| GPS-GPetShop_Cool_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | $4,894.25 | $24,804.21 | 443 | 3,552 | 19.7% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n| Petkin-BigNThick_Pet_Wipes_Large-MULTI-Branded-SP… | $2,530.85 | $15,278.01 | 701 | 1,728 | 16.6% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n| GPS-Chillz_Pet_Pad-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $3,157.08 | $13,424.75 | 296 | 1,980 | 23.5% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n| Arrow-CatchAll-MULTI-Branded-SP-Phrase | $1,140.61 | $13,246.08 | 585 | 1,376 | 8.6% | protect budget and expand exact/high-intent coverage |\n\n## Optimization / Reduction Candidates\n\n| campaign | spend | sales | orders | clicks | ACOS | recommended action |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Petkin-Paw_Wipes_Orange-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $2,434.95 | $2,687.77 | 153 | 883 | 90.6% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Hornady-RAPiD_Gun_Safes-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | $1,894.61 | $2,446.69 | 14 | 733 | 77.4% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Petkin-Pet_Dental_Wipes-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $1,888.88 | $1,821.15 | 127 | 515 | 103.7% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Petkin-Pet_Fingertip_Tooth_Wipes-MULTI-NB-SP-Exact | $1,176.69 | $1,260.44 | 87 | 350 | 93.4% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Petkin-BigNThick_Pet_Wipes_Large-MULTI-NB-SP-Phra… | $1,041.94 | $910.53 | 52 | 266 | 114.4% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Petkin-Pet_Dental_Wipes-MULTI-NB-SP-Phrase | $875.83 | $932.19 | 66 | 350 | 94.0% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Hornady-Fireproof_Keypad_Safe-B09TQ2CW9L-NB-SP-Ph… | $654.14 | $1,039.75 | 5 | 345 | 62.9% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n| Hornady-Auto_Charge_Pro_Powder_Measure-B081DJPYM8… | $632.56 | $185.85 | 3 | 263 | 340.4% | negate, pause, or reduce bid after checking strategic value |\n\n## Recommendations\n\n1. Reallocate budget toward entities with orders, controlled ACOS, and stable sales contribution.\n2. Reduce or pause high-spend zero-order entities first to release inefficient spend.\n3. For entities with orders but high ACOS, lower bids by 15-30% and monitor for 3-5 days.\n4. If the requested bid, budget, placement, or advertised-ASIN fields are missing from the business data, add those fields before making exact operational changes.\n"
