          "label": "A",
          "content": "> **Assumptions applied to this analysis — please confirm or adjust if needed:**\n> - **Time range**: Most recent 63 days (2026-03-07 → 2026-05-08) to cover your \"60+ days\" request.\n> - **Meaningful spend**: Total Spend ≥ $10 over the period (conservative threshold to exclude near-zero-budget ASINs).\n> - **Negligible sales**: Total Sales = $0 or < $1 over the full period.\n> - **Scope**: Actively running ads only (productAd, adGroup, and campaign all in `enabled` state).\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 Key Findings\n\n1. **20 ASINs** have accumulated meaningful ad spend with zero sales over the past 63 days — all are recommended for pausing.\n2. **$516.50 in combined spend** has been wasted on these non-converting ASINs, with no return.\n3. The top 3 offenders alone account for **$253.71** (~49% of the wasted budget): B07W8X7WWL ($103.69), B005BDCF40 ($93.81), and B005BE47D6 ($56.21).\n4. Despite generating **390,323 total impressions and 380 clicks** across these 20 ASINs, not a single conversion was recorded — suggesting structural issues (listing quality, pricing, competition, or product-market fit) rather than just ad targeting problems.\n\n---\n\n## 📋 Pause Candidates — Full List\n\n\n| ASIN | SKU | Spend (USD) | Sales (USD) | Orders | Clicks | Impressions | Pause? |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B07W8X7WWL\">B07W8X7WWL</Link> | CASKU24286_MFN | 103.69 | 0 | 0 | 26 | 7912 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B005BDCF40\">B005BDCF40</Link> | CASKU24281_MFN | 93.81 | 0 | 0 | 45 | 11833 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B005BE47D6\">B005BE47D6</Link> | CASKU24284_MFN | 56.21 | 0 | 0 | 34 | 9351 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B09THMPDPK\">B09THMPDPK</Link> | CASKU27100 | 30.68 | 0 | 0 | 22 | 5225 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0BB54CL26\">B0BB54CL26</Link> | CASKU26803_MFN | 25.53 | 0 | 0 | 16 | 5635 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B078J36HYK\">B078J36HYK</Link> | CASKU21060 | 19.85 | 0 | 0 | 15 | 3333 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0CN2KVXVZ\">B0CN2KVXVZ</Link> | CASKU27253-2 | 18.22 | 0 | 0 | 18 | 6879 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0CN2H235P\">B0CN2H235P</Link> | CASKU27268-2_MFN | 17.62 | 0 | 0 | 25 | 4318 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0CX9J2WPF\">B0CX9J2WPF</Link> | CASKU27620 | 17.56 | 0 | 0 | 19 | 6256 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0C443S59D\">B0C443S59D</Link> | CASKU27249 | 16.22 | 0 | 0 | 20 | 6714 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0F1Z49KCN\">B0F1Z49KCN</Link> | 850057649895_Guardian_FBA_95_VT | 15.8 | 0 | 0 | 23 | 5779 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0CXB3981H\">B0CXB3981H</Link> | CASKU27626 | 13.08 | 0 | 0 | 21 | 6371 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0BCHDQ87V\">B0BCHDQ87V</Link> | CASKU26815 | 12.17 | 0 | 0 | 5 | 3332 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0F1Z6QMDQ\">B0F1Z6QMDQ</Link> | 850057649925_Guardian_FBA_99_VT | 11.49 | 0 | 0 | 15 | 6300 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0D8JQY4QM\">B0D8JQY4QM</Link> | CASKU27672 | 11.27 | 0 | 0 | 10 | 2181 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0F1Z5LSZG\">B0F1Z5LSZG</Link> | 850057649765_Guardian_FBA_91_VT | 11.23 | 0 | 0 | 15 | 5005 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B01F209RSI\">B01F209RSI</Link> | CASKU25893_MFN | 11.05 | 0 | 0 | 7 | 482 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0BXFY51TQ\">B0BXFY51TQ</Link> | CASKU27130 | 10.83 | 0 | 0 | 12 | 2751 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0CPKD1RC5\">B0CPKD1RC5</Link> | CASKU27544_MFN | 10.19 | 0 | 0 | 17 | 976 | Yes |\n| <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0F1Z549DJ\">B0F1Z549DJ</Link> | 850057649918_Guardian_FBA_98_VT | 10 | 0 | 0 | 12 | 4941 | Yes |\n\n**Summary**: **20 ASINs** | **$516.50 combined wasted spend** | **0 orders** across all 20 over 63 days\n\n---\n\n## 💡 Recommendations\n\n### 1. Pause Ad Promotion Immediately (High Priority)\nAll 20 ASINs listed above should have their **productAds paused** to stop the bleeding. Prioritize the top spenders first:\n\n| Priority | ASIN | Spend (USD) | Action |\n|----------|------|-------------|--------|\n| 🔴 Urgent | <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B07W8X7WWL\">B07W8X7WWL</Link> | $103.69 | Pause immediately |\n| 🔴 Urgent | <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B005BDCF40\">B005BDCF40</Link> | $93.81 | Pause immediately |\n| 🔴 Urgent | <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B005BE47D6\">B005BE47D6</Link> | $56.21 | Pause immediately |\n| 🟠 High | <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B09THMPDPK\">B09THMPDPK</Link> | $30.68 | Pause soon |\n| 🟠 High | <Link entity=\"asin\" name=\"B0BB54CL26\">B0BB54CL26</Link> | $25.53 | Pause soon |\n\n### 2. Diagnose Root Cause Before Re-activating\nZero sales over 63 days despite clicks and impressions is a strong signal of **non-ad issues**. Before re-enabling ads for any of these ASINs, investigate:\n- **Listing quality**: Are the title, images, bullet points, and A+ content competitive?\n- **Pricing**: Is the price significantly above comparable products?\n- **Buy Box**: Are these ASINs winning the Buy Box? (Note: several SKUs are tagged `_MFN`, indicating merchant-fulfilled — Buy Box win rate may be low.)\n- **Inventory**: Are these products actually in stock and shippable?\n- **Product-market fit**: Some of these may simply not have sufficient demand in the current market.\n\n### 3. Special Attention: MFN SKUs\n7 of the 20 ASINs have `_MFN` suffixes (merchant-fulfilled), including the top 2 spenders. MFN listings often struggle to win the Buy Box against FBA competitors, which can explain zero conversions even with ad impressions and clicks. Consider:\n- Switching to FBA fulfillment if feasible, or\n- Keeping these paused until Buy Box eligibility improves.\n\n### 4. Re-evaluation Criteria\nIf you choose to re-test any of these ASINs after fixing listing/fulfillment issues, set a clear **spend cap and review trigger** — e.g., pause again if Spend exceeds $15 with fewer than 1 order within a 2-week window."
